N:langsmith
D:[langsmith] Instrument, trace, evaluate, and review LLM applications with LangSmith by choosing the right workflow first: debugging traces, offline evals, online feedback/review queues, prompt-registry work, or multi-service trace propagation. Use when users mention LangSmith, LangChain tracing, @traceable/traceable, wrap_openai/wrapOpenAI, datasets, annotation queues, experiment comparison, prompt hub, run trees, or production confidence for an AI feature. Not for generic alerting/SLO design, deployment orchestration, or runtime guardrails outside LangSmith.
G:langsmith langchain tracing observability evaluation llm-monitoring prompt-hub datasets openevals traceable wrap_openai wrapOpenAI feedback annotation-queue experiment run-tree trace-propagation

U[6]:
  Add or review LangSmith tracing for chat apps, RAG pipelines, tool-calling backends, or agents
  Build offline evals before a prompt/model/app change ships
  Add online feedback, annotation queues, or review rubrics for production traces
  Compare prompt or model variants with experiment runs
  Decide whether Prompt Hub should own the prompt lifecycle
  Correlate traces across services, workers, or agent/tool boundaries

S[5]{n,action,details}:
  1,Label workflow,Classify app shape runtime request type current evidence and confidence problem before touching APIs
  2,Choose mode,Pick debugging traces offline evals online review prompt-registry work multi-service propagation or audit/gap review
  3,Choose surface,Select wrappers decorators tracing_context manual trace blocks header propagation or CLI export flows
  4,Design packet,Return required env/config metadata IDs dataset/evaluator/review design and verification step
  5,Route out,Send generic observability deployment or runtime-policy work to adjacent skills instead of overclaiming LangSmith

R[5]:
  Treat LangSmith as a trace/eval/review substrate not the whole production control plane
  Preserve run_id trace_id project env tags and metadata deliberately
  Use the smallest useful instrumentation surface first
  Separate deterministic evaluators LLM judges and human review instead of pretending one replaces the others
  Add flush or wait behavior for short-lived scripts workers and CLIs

E[3]{type,code}:
  Trace debugging packet,mode=debugging traces plus wrappers/decorators project tags metadata and flush step
  Eval packet,mode=offline evals plus dataset evaluators experiment prefix baseline/candidate comparison
  Review packet,mode=online feedback plus feedback keys annotation queue rubric and run_id preservation
